data.description: Welcome to this stunning and picturesque property nestled in the heart of Tuscumbia, AL! Prepare to be captivated by this absolutely beautiful, stately 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home situated on a sprawling 0.9-acre lot within the city limits. This is a truly unique split-level home that exudes charm at every turn. The attention to detail is impeccable, with custom black concrete countertops, boasting a unique custom backsplash, sleek black appliances all while overlooking the beautiful backyard! The bedrooms within this home are full of personality and charm! The downstairs master is a true sanctuary, offering a harmonious blend of comfort and style making it the ideal retreat to unwind after a long day. The bathrooms are equally luxurious, with modern fixtures and elegant finishes that evoke a spa-like atmosphere. Just minutes from Downtown Tuscumbia, Spring Park, and Muscle Shoals this home is surrounded by amenities, dining options, and recreational activities. Schedule a tour today!
